                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-420" type="given" value="RALPH"></interp>RALPH HEATON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I produce the certificate of Smith's former conviction, which I got at Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
